data.description: 3 bedroom 2 bath Barndominium is in excellent shape. Featuring an open living-kitchen floorplan. With beautiful stained concrete floors throughout. Lovely solid surface counter tops in kitchen. You will love the large primary bedroom with walk in closet and walk in shower. Nice covered carport and a fenced backyard. Large covered front porch Bonus of extra insulation in attic. Only minutes from Granbury Lake with boat ramp in community.
